reviews.text: Charming bartender gave good recommendations and info. on the selected drinks. Impressive experience on my first whisky of the night!  Better book in advance.

Heard there is a new Whisky Lounge in Kwun Tong referred by a friend of mine. I got a chance to visit Prime House after a day of work finally. The in-house Whisky Ambassador introduced several whiskies based on my preferences and experience. Very Nice! Actually, it is a good place to hangout with friends. If you wanna enjoy your private moment, this is also a wonderful place for you to enjoy a glass of whisky.

A really chill place in kwun tong to hang out with my friends.  Got really nice cocktails and the bartenders are very friendly.  I've learnt more about how to taste whiskies properly.  Certainly will visit again!

A cozy whisky lounge with professional in-house Whisky Ambassadors. The ambassadors are able to introduce different types of whiskies across the globe and can suggest a best-fit whisky that may fit your mood and preference.
Impossible to find. We were up on the 11th and we saw the logo, but doors were closed on a Thursday at 6pm

reviews.text: 我只可以講Prime House Whisky Lounge 係暫時我去過香港既飲酒地方數一數二最好，如果對Whisky或Coffee有興趣既朋友一定要到！有兩個好有經驗既Co-Founder，佢地真係好有心去做好呢間店，我飲住咁學識好多野！最重要係香港人因為好多因素彼此少左好多交流，係呢度用酒打破隔膜，非常好既環境同威士忌，仲有咖啡同Cocktail，全部都得來不易因為每一個Product背景佢地都付出好多！非常值得去欣賞同享受！下次會試你地Lunch Menu！我同女朋友今日真係好難忘！因為一切都係緣份，好開心認識呢一度，你地要Keep住！一路堅持一定成功！
